Package: nrc.gov
Title: NRC Nuclear Regulatory Commission Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for U.S. Nuclear Regulatory Commission public data.
    Access reactor status, inspection findings, performance indicators, and action matrix data.
    Includes LLM context injection via nrc_context().
